int a[]=new int a[5];

Opearations on ArrayList
---------------------------
1) How to declare list
2) How to add elements/values to array list.
3) Find size of array list
4) Read values from ArrayList
5) Insert a new element in the middle of arraylist
6) remove elements/values from arrayList.

