read pairs from hashmap

JDBC --JAVA DATABSE CONNECTIVITY
---------------------------------
 Pre-requisite
 --------------
 1) Download databse driver(.jar file)
 2) Add driver jar to your project
 
 Steps to write JDBC PROGRAM
 -----------------------------
 INSERT,UPDATE,DELETE --DML COMMANDS
 1) create a connection
 2) create a query/statement
 3) Execute statement/query
 4) close connection
 
 SELECT -- DATA RETRIEVAL	/DQL DATA QUERY LANGUAGE
 1) create a connection
 2) create a query/statement
 3) Execute statement/query
 4) Store the results in result set
 5) close connection
 

 
 
 